RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHURCHILL DOWNS RACE 11 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 89. Maiden Special Weight Purse 120000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 119 lbs. (Preference To Horses That Have Not Started For Less Than $50,000).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: I'M A MESS bumped with an outer rival at the start, laid off of the pace along the inside under snug restraint around the first turn, fanned from the four to six path entering the lane, rallied to bid at the furlong grounds, forged an advantage from an inner bidding counterpart soon after and inched away. ENIGMATIC stalked along the inside, loomed a danger with run from the pocket around the far turn, brushed an outer rival to take aim in the four path in upper stretch, bid with an outer foe at the furlong grounds, but was headed by that one in the process, failed to keep pace late and saved place. GENETICS laid off of the pace two wide and between horses, was outmoved to trail the field entering the lane in the six path, tipped outwardly in upper stretch, then unleashed a strong late kick outside of foes to miss reaching place. CLASS ACT bobbled and bumped with an inner rival at the start before being brushed between foes soon after, trailed around both turns, fanned to the seven path entering the lane, rallied to bid for show in the final furlong but was outkicked late. AMERICA'S VOW pursued from midpack two wide and between horses and chased evenly. MURPHY'S GIFT pressed two wide, bid in the three path entering the lane, dueled through upper stretch but was outkicked by outer rivals at the furlong grounds and gave way. HER BEST FRIEND pursued four wide, ranged up to attempted a bid entering the lane, but was brushed by an inner rival in upper stretch, yielded between horses in the aftermath, yet sustained a chase on his left lead late. HAPPY TALK failed to menace three wide. CHARLOTTESAPPROVAL saved ground in midpack, chased and lacked a bid between horses in the final sixteenth. LOVELAND set the pace along the inside, dueled with an outer bidder through upper stretch but weakened at the furlong grounds. CARARRA tracked three wide and faded between horses in upper stretch.
